metadata.name: Predictions and Predicaments
metadata.description:
Now streaming : 'Life', as we call it. The yellow door of happiness has its tempt but the behind picture has its own red carpet shuffle of ups and downs. There is nothing wrong with hoping for brights, but the acceptance & normalisation of the dark tones is equally important to embrace it completely.

Size : 6667 px X 5000 px
Medium : Digital
